column2: SELECT  s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.subClass, s.class_person, s.comments_person, g.*, e.bpt FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON s.specObjID= g.specObjID  LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON g.specObjID = e.specObjID WHERE htmid*# & # < (# * #) AND  s.class <> &&& AND  s.plateSN2 > #
